Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在凌晨兩點了  您要回家嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's two o'clock in the morning. Would you like to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我待會兒就出去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, yes, I'll be out in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的肝再生速度不夠快\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}His liver is just not regenerating fast enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那具體是什么意思\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What does that mean, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他需要移植  否則會死\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He needs a transplant, or he'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么時候  -幾天之內\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- How soon? - Days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b1\3c&H000000&\shad1\bord0\an3}待移植者瀕臨死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們將他列為了{\u1}1號情況{\u0}\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We've made him Status 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們應該能為他找到合適的肝臟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm optimistic we'll find him a suitable liver.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受者名單是機密\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The recipient list is classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有您二位政府成員知情\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're the only two members of the administration who've been briefed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一夫人知道了嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Is the First Lady aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我今天下午告訴她了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes, I informed her this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以進來嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道很晚了  但他們說你沒睡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I know it's late, but they said you were up, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  我就是一天都沒吃東西了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, I know. I just hadn't eaten all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm sure you haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-來點沙拉嗎  -好啊  謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Would you like some salad? - Sure. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗蘭克的事  真是可怕\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's scary, about Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗蘭西斯是個斗士\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, Francis is a fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望我能問他的建議\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I wish I could ask his advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明早要跟佩特羅夫通電話了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I have my call with Petrov in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對計劃頗為了解  這點我有自信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I feel good about my understanding of the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我擔心的是他在電話里威脅我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}My concern is him railroading me on the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你希望我跟你一起打嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, would you like me to be on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多個人聽聽\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}An extra set of ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道凱茜會有什么想法\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't... I don't know how Cathy would feel about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不非得讓她知道啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, she doesn't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以在這里聽\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I could just listen from up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你有麻煩  或許我可以發點建議過去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And maybe I could type a note if you get into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...對總統的恢復閉口不談\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}...tight-lipped on the president's recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到目前  據報他情況穩定\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}As of now, he's reported to be in stable condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚無媒體被允許進入醫院\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No press has been allowed into the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共和黨候選人威爾·康威\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Republican presidential hopeful Will Conway
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早在亞利桑那州一場集會上提到了總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}spoke of the president at a rally in Arizona this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我經常批評安德伍德總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've criticized President Underwood often.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但此刻  他是我們的總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But right now, he's our president...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天來吧  我們沒油了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Come back tomorrow. We're all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}兩黨要團結一致\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}...and we have to pull together, both sides of the aisle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們今天沒油了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We're all out for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  明天再來吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Sorry, come back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-沒油了  沒油了  -不是吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- We're all out, guys. We're all out. - Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天再來吧  我們今天沒油了  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Come back tomorrow. We're all out for today, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真扯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能從你這兒吸幾加侖嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Can I siphon a couple of gallons from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五十塊  我已經沒油了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Fifty bucks. I'm running on fumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還得送孩子上學  送老公上班\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I gotta get my kids to school, and my husband to work--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八十塊  兩加侖\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Eighty bucks, two gallons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  幫不了你  抱歉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Sorry, I can't help you. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.89,0:08:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接通了嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The line's open?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫斯科就等您了  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Moscow is ready when you are, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放在這里就好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You can set it up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小抄\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}My Cliff Notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我準備好了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統先生  您已與佩特羅夫總統接通\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mr. President, you're on with President Petrov.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄羅斯舉國上下都在為總統的康復祈禱\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}All of Russia is praying for the president's recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請代我轉達對安德伍德夫人的問候\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I hope you will extend my warm thoughts to Mrs. Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I certainly will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是勇敢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're a brave man
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在如此艱難的時刻接手\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}to take over during such difficult times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想確保\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I just want to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們找到可行方案解決這場油價...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}we find a manageable resolution to this oil--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讀過你寫的一些書  總統先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've read some of your books, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛讀完《學會學習》\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I just finished Learning to Learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不錯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一章關于想象的令我很感興趣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}There was a chapter on visualization that really interested me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  是學生可用的工具  幫助他們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes, it's a... A tool for students. It helps them--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想請你想象一下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I would like you to visualize something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你站在苔原上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now, you're standing in the tundra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大風  暴雪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Um, wind, snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機器在鉆透冰層\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}machines drilling through the ice,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長長的管線延伸至遠處的地平線  你能想象嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}long pipelines stretching to the horizon. Do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想談西伯利亞  我很樂意...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If you want to talk about Siberia, I'm more than happy to--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  你不是在想象\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, no, no. You're not visualizing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副總統先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉上你的眼睛\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  閉上了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}All right. They're closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  那么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Good. Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象工人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}picture the men
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在鉆井和管線上工作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}working those drills and pipelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們什么樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What do they look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大棉衣  戴手套  穿著靴子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Um, heavy coats, gloves, boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Are they...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中國人嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Chinese?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧  當我想象的時候\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You see, when I picture this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不到中國人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't see Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我同意  中國的控制權越少越好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I agree with you. The less control the Chinese have, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你為什么把米爾金送去中國\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Then why did you send Milkin to China?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不肯跟我們談判\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You weren't negotiating with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們覺得或許他們的運氣會更好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We thought they might have more luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的要求會讓我們陷入比之前更糟的境地\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Their demands would leave us worse off than we were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以讓國際貨幣基金組織拿出一半的救市資金\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I can get the IMF to provide half the bailout.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可以制衡中國對開采權的要求\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This would counteract the Chinese demands for drilling rights--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想挑撥我們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You are playing us off each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mr. President--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:11:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得  你是自不量力了  布萊斯先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I think you're in over your head, Mr. Blythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,容我解釋一下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If you would just give me a chance to elaborate--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憑什么讓你解釋\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Why give you a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對俄羅斯  對中國有什么了解\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What do you know about Russia? About China?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經聽過了...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've been briefed on--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  但是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Forgive me, but, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不愿跟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't feel comfortable
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統以外的人進行談判\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}negotiating with anyone other than the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等他康復  或許我們可以談談\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}When he recovers, perhaps he and I can speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們完事了嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So, are we finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.34,0:11:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統情況很糟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The president's in very bad shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多嚴重\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How serious is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他需要肝臟移植\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He needs a liver transplant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I wasn't aware that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好習慣跟我磋商\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You better get used to negotiating with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果總統死了  那就是你和我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If the president dies, it's you and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則沒得可談\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}or nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  總統先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}My apologies, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:12:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無意侮辱你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I didn't intend to insult you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們繼續協商  我只求這個\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let's keep a dialogue open. That's all I'm asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想給你一份應對中方要求的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'd like the opportunity to present you with a detailed proposal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具體提議\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}countering the Chinese demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會讓國務卿杜蘭特跟你的外交部長接洽\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll have Secretary Durant work with your foreign minister,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我們再談\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and then we'll take it from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣可以嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Are you open to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待看到你的提議\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I look forward to reviewing your proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  總統先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  這消息我們還不希望透露出去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Sir, we didn't want that to get out to the press yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美國人民反正也該知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The American people deserve to know, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  俄羅斯人是見軟就欺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Sir, the Russians don't respond well to weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在他們知道總統...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now that they know that the president--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽到他說愿意協商了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You heard him say he's open to negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為這是進展\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'd say that's progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四天了  還沒有嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Four days and still nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有記者招待會  沒有通報\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No press conference, no briefing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得讓他們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We have to let them conduct
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按自己的步調進行調查\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}their investigation on their own terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好像我們被蒙在鼓里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Feels like we're being shut out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅僅是聯調局\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This isn't just the bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們還得跟國土安全部協調\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They have to coordinate with Homeland
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-確保敏感...  -扯淡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- and make sure nothing sensitive-- - That's bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古德溫有什么情況你不希望我們知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}There's something about Goodwin that you don't want us to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你一樣想知道他這么做的動機\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I wanna know why he did this just as much as you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們得讓聯調局做他們的工作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But we've gotta let the FBI do its job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我去看他時是同一個論調\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Same theory as when I visited him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是他達成認罪協議之前  是嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And that was before he struck the plea, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我鼓勵他認罪的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I encouraged him to plead guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的宣稱毫無依據\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}His claims were unsubstantiated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我們說說你去見古德溫之前\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Tell us about your meeting with the president
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟總統的見面\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}prior to that meeting with Goodwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盧卡斯拜托我調查  我就調查了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Lucas asked me to investigate. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此采訪了安德伍德\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That involved an interview with Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還留著筆記嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You still have your notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有搜查令我不會交出筆記\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No notes without a warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媒體  沒日沒夜地打\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The press. Calling non-stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們建議調查期間你不要跟任何人...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We suggest you don't speak to anyone while we're still--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心  我完全不想被扯進來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Don't worry. I don't have any interest in getting dragged into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去把筆記找出來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let me go dig up those notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布萊斯  他告訴佩特羅夫總統需要移植\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Blythe... He told Petrov the president needs a transplant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他為什么要那么做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Why would he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩特羅夫把他氣到了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Petrov got under his skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是為什么我們本該按你丈夫的計劃來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This is why we should've carried out your husband's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們給了莫斯科太多操作的空間\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We're giving Moscow too much room to maneuver--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們別談論無法改變的事了  道格\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let's not debate what we can't change, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果莫斯科知道了  我們就得通知媒體\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If Moscow knows, we'll have to notify the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明天就說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We're doing that tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由薩克遜醫生來做通告\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Dr. Saxon will do the briefing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我來吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:14:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是由第一夫人來說的好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's better coming from the First Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我同意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這事我們也得應對一下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We need to address this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局在古德溫家找到了他的遺書\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The FBI found Goodwin's notes in his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以給處理掉嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Can we make them disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  已經被收為證據了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, it's already been catalogued.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得先一步采取行動控制輿論\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We need to get out ahead of it and control the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  給我弄一份目前為止的調查報告\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}All right. Get me a copy and report on the investigation so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想見他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I wanna see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The president.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特勤局不許我進去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The Secret Service still won't let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請允許斯坦普先生見我丈夫\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'd like Mr. Stamper to have access to my husband, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們有嚴格命令  夫人  只有您\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We have strict orders, ma'am. Only you and--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我親自打給副總統嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Would you like me to call the vice president myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道格拉斯  這位年輕人會送你進去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Douglas, this young man will escort you to his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-幾點了  -7點剛過\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- What time is it? - It's a little past 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  先生  是道格\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Sir? Sir, it's Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然他睜開了眼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Just because his eyes are open
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不代表他的意識完全清醒了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}doesn't mean he's fully conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肝功能不足\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Insufficient liver function.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的大腦泡在一堆未處理的氨中\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}His brain is swimming in a pool of unprocessed ammonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他能看到什么  大概也是嚴重的幻覺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If he's seeing anything, it's probably severe hallucinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他多久能得到肝臟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How long until he has a liver?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能得要幾小時  可能要幾天\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Could be hours. Could be days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是名單上第三位\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's number three on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三名\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Number three?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名單按需排序\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's prioritized in terms of need
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是1號情況的第一位\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and who was listed first as a Status 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是美國總統啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's the President of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是法律\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司法部長要辭職\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The attorney general is resigning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這條加入今天下午的新聞發布稿中\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Add that to the press release for this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是她的決定還是副總統的  -我的決定\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Uh, her decision or the vice president's? - My decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古德溫的證人保護計劃是司法部的責任\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Goodwin's WITSEC was a DOJ responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得找人背鍋\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We needed a head to roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先是她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}First hers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}then yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明天辭職\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You'll resign tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道格  我知道你現在壓力很大  但是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Doug, I know you're under a lot of pressure, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.41,0:18:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你發了那張南軍士兵照片\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You sent the photo of the rebel soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私人手機  沒在這里發\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Personal phone, off the premises.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:18:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是有人黑了我的賬戶什么的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You know, maybe somebody hacked my account or something--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真要再這么對我撒謊嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Are you really gonna keep lying to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以叫人逮捕你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I could have you arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我寧可你低調離去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But I'd rather you go quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道些事  道格\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I know things, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你證明不了什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Nothing you can prove.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再威脅我啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now, threaten me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中國如果不加入  提議就沒戲\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}There's no proposal without China's involvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茜試了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now, Cathy's tried,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她跟他們的關系不是特別好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but she doesn't have the best relationship with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許她需要幫助\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Maybe she needs some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫助  怎么說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Help? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你介意我抽煙嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Do you mind if I smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然不\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我十年前戒了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I quit about ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪喬莉逼我的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Marjory forced me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是那么好聞\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Ah, still smells delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪喬莉死時什么樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What was it like when Marjory died?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, well, it was, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  如果你不愿意我們不用談這個\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm sorry. We don't have to talk about it if you don't want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  沒事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們當時已經數月沒有真正聊過了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We hadn't had a real conversation in... in months.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的神智已經不清楚了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Her mind was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她最終死時\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}When she finally died,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好像被砍掉根肋骨\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}it felt like a limb had been hacked off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...痛不欲生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I felt... devastated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也如釋重負\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But I also felt relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對我母親的感覺就是這樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That's what I feel about my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:21:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不...我都沒想起來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, I hadn't-- It hadn't even occurred to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了弗蘭克  你母親也病了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You have Frank and your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親去世時  我幾乎崩潰了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}When my father died, it destroyed me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但想到我母親時  我毫無感覺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but when I think about Mother, I feel nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你們不親近嗎  -不\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- You two aren't close? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對弗蘭西斯也是這種感覺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And I feel the same about Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無感覺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.37,0:21:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道這聽起來很可怕\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I know that must sound awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這很難接受\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's a lot to process.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這沒有正誤之分\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}There's no right way or wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-等下  慢著  -不\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Wait, hold on. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪喬莉不會同意的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Marjory wouldn't approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛說到哪了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We got sidetracked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  中國\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes. China.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.94,0:21:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個主意  如果你相信我能做好的話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I have an idea, if you can trust me to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我賭上命相信你  克萊爾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'd trust you with my goddamn life, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Comment c'est elle?{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.99,0:22:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會想知道的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You don't want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝點水吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Water?{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用  媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Non, ca va, mamon.{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.28,0:22:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不希望你們中暑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Je veux pas vous laisse attraper un coup de chaleur, vous voyez?{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來拿  謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I got it. Ah, merci.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.56,0:22:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}C'est qui?{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.72,0:22:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒誰  同事而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Non, c'est un colleague de moi.{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.55,0:22:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你  媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mamon.{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉安\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}LeAnn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.49,0:22:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找你可真難\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You are a tough guy to track down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你來干什么  -你要趕飛機\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- What are you doing here? - You have a plane to catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一夫人需要你的幫助\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The First Lady needs your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.91,0:22:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想和他們有任何瓜葛\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't want to have anything to do with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.64,0:22:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論你對總統的看法如何\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Whatever you think of the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對祖國依然負有責任\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}you still have a duty to your country.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算他在我離開白宮的那天去世\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Even if he dies, the day I walked out the White House,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也向自己承諾過不會回去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I promised myself I wasn't going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.31,0:22:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你連我們的計劃都不知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You don't even know what we have in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.32,0:22:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無所謂  我不去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It doesn't matter. I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:22:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想請你離開\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'd like you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.71,0:23:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是基本情況的材料\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Here's your briefing materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.34,0:23:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒聽見我說嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're not hearing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真應該看一眼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You should really take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.88,0:23:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的競選會完蛋的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Her campaign would be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.28,0:23:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你父母會怎么想\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And what would your parents think?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去就像你要利用他受傷...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It looks like you're taking advantage of the fact that he's--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康威仍在進行競選活動\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Conway is still campaigning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.49,0:23:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是共和黨人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's a Republican
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.55,0:23:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他的提名已經十拿九穩\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and he's already wrapped up his nomination.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.07,0:23:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我們不一樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Apples and oranges.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.95,0:23:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們什么都不做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We are gonna lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.74,0:23:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪著一個不省人事的人干坐著  會輸的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}if we sit still, to a guy who's unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.78,0:23:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希瑟說得對  安德伍德在大賺同情分\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Heather's right. Underwood's scoring major sympathy points.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.93,0:23:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在接下來的七個州里  他在六個州領先\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's ahead in six of the next seven states.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.70,0:23:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得繼續施壓\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We need to keep the pressure up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.02,0:23:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄羅斯  油價\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Russia, gas prices...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.62,0:23:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻擊一位正與死神搏斗的總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Attack a president who's fighting for his life?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.98,0:23:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你們來開會不是來辯論的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I didn't call this meeting to debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.09,0:23:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要奪回那些州\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I want those states back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們開始準備活動和媒體造勢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So let's start organizing events and media hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明早之前  確定初步預算和安排\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Prelim budgets and schedules, by tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.44,0:24:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對于古德溫的動機  人們有多種猜測\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}There has been much speculation as to Goodwin's motivations.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.35,0:24:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛西婭\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Cynthia.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.45,0:24:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古德溫的事進展如何\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Where are we on Goodwin?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.52,0:24:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經搞定了保安\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The security guy's taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.95,0:24:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他沒看見你們在一起\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He never saw the two of you together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.99,0:24:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那其他人呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What about others?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.07,0:24:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據他所知  沒有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}None that he knows of.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.41,0:24:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們又不能四處詢問\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But it's not like we can ask around.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.89,0:24:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在2013年11月\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}In November of 2013,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.46,0:24:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴恩斯女士被華府地鐵撞擊身亡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Ms. Barnes was struck by a D.C. metrorail train.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.60,0:24:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,華府警方將其定性為一場事故\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}D.C. police classified it as an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.41,0:24:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人推測...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Some have speculated that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.79,0:24:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐吧  雷米\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Have a seat, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.92,0:25:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗蘭克的事我很遺憾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Sorry about Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.83,0:25:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  省省吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, please, don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.10,0:25:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經聽夠了人們說他們很遺憾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've had enough people say they're sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.76,0:25:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道你不是真心的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and I know you don't mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.21,0:25:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒法按你希望的那樣幫你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I can't help you the way you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.40,0:25:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉安告訴我她已經跟你說得很明白了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}LeAnn told me she was very clear with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.50,0:25:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.71,0:25:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔斯克比我更不想幫你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Tusk wants to help you even less than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.89,0:25:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是誰在幫誰  雷米\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, nobody's doing any favors here, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.87,0:25:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他會從中獲得一大筆錢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's going to get very rich from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.76,0:25:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什么不親自跟他說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Why don't you speak to him yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.20,0:25:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他不會聽我的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Because he won't listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.02,0:25:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這必須聽起來像是你的主意  而不是我的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This needs to seem like your idea, not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.81,0:25:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也會撈上一大筆的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And you'll make a killing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.73,0:25:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要錢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't need the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.18,0:25:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你現在在乎的是別的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Because you care about other things now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.79,0:25:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如杰姬\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Like Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.82,0:25:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你必須做成此事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Which is why you'll make this happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.56,0:25:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我當初跟鄧巴說了弗蘭克的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If I had told Dunbar about Frank...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.68,0:25:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說他知道洗錢的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}about how he knew about the laundering,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.46,0:25:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就當不了總統  我們現在也不會站在這兒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}he wouldn't be president and we wouldn't be standing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.58,0:25:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你沒有  你現在也說不了了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But you didn't and you can't now,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.95,0:25:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以現在是這樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}so here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.85,0:26:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩小時  我們毫無進展\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Two hours and we got nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.37,0:26:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只想聽中國的反應\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}All he wants to hear is China.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.04,0:26:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告訴他北京方面不回應\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I told him Beijing is not responsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.94,0:26:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他根本不在乎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He doesn't give a damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.14,0:26:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一夫人給他提過醒了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The First Lady put a bug in his ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.47,0:26:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管她說了什么  他鐵了心不聽我們的了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, whatever bug she put in there won't crawl out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.33,0:26:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會安排次會面  只有你我他三人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll set up a meeting. Just you, me and him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.28,0:26:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕一次會面是不夠的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't think a meeting is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.82,0:26:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的副總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We have a vice president
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.14,0:26:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道他在干什么  道格\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that does not know what he is doing, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.60,0:26:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他必須把外交事務\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He needs to completely turn over
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.42,0:26:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部移交給國務院\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}all diplomatic affairs to the State Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.48,0:26:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-否則我完全無能為力  -現在不行\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Otherwise, my hands are tied. - Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.63,0:26:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常緊急\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.67,0:26:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們結束后  我會去找你的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}When we're finished, I will come and find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.48,0:26:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您能讓我們單獨談談嗎  國務卿女士\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Could you give us a few moments, Madam Secretary?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.52,0:26:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-賽斯  你太過分了  -沒關系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Seth, you're out of line! - It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.46,0:26:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我打電話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.29,0:26:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會的  謝謝  凱茜\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I will. Thank you, Cathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.96,0:26:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.08,0:26:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你他媽在干什么  -你不能開除我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- What the fuck are you doing? - You can't fire me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.40,0:26:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能打斷我和國務卿的會面\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You don't interrupt a meeting with the Secretary of State.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.79,0:26:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以終結鄧巴的競選\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I can end Dunbar's campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.81,0:26:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就結束掉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We can end it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.86,0:26:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.68,0:26:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我做到  你能讓我留下嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If I deliver, will you keep me on?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.71,0:26:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得先告訴我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You tell me how first.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.68,0:27:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐吧  瑪莎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Have a seat, Martha.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.79,0:27:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我重新考慮了一下你的辭職\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've had second thoughts about your resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.77,0:27:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還想繼續當司法部長嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Would you like to remain as attorney general?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.15,0:27:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我想\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes, I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.05,0:27:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  道格\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.47,0:27:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希瑟·鄧巴有沒有告訴過你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Did Heather Dunbar inform you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.74,0:27:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她和盧卡斯·古德溫見過面\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}of a meeting between herself and Lucas Goodwin?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.50,0:27:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要讓我的下屬審問我嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're having me interrogated by my own subordinates?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.50,0:27:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能保住工作  他們才是你的屬下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They only work for you if you keep your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.06,0:27:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我建議你回答他們的問題\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I suggest you answer their questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.66,0:27:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要我的律師在場\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'd like a lawyer present.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.12,0:27:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我提醒你  女士\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let me remind you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.66,0:27:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒告知我們已經構成了隱瞞證據\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Failing to have informed us constitutes withholding of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.64,0:27:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希瑟是我的朋友\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Heather is a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.23,0:27:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常簡單  瑪莎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's very simple, Martha.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.69,0:27:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我們合作  你就繼續當司法部長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You work with us, you stay on as AG.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.13,0:27:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不合作  我們就起訴\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You don't, we prosecute.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.05,0:28:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士們先生們  美國第一夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Ladies and Gentlemen, the First Lady of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.55,0:28:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家下午好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Good afternoon, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.21,0:28:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想向大家通報我丈夫康復的最新情況\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'd like to update you on my husband's recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.39,0:28:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統的醫療團隊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The President's medical team
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.04,0:28:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚做出了全面的評估\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}gave me a full assessment last night
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.41,0:28:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們最后的結論是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and they have come to the conclusion
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.24,0:28:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統需要肝移植\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that the President is in need of a liver transplant
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.69,0:28:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能活下去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}if he's to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.66,0:28:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我請求全國與我共同祈禱\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm asking the nation to pray with me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.17,0:28:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗朗西斯能盡快等到一個健康的肝臟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that a healthy liver makes its way to Francis soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.69,0:28:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  請等一下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm sorry. A moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.43,0:28:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.13,0:28:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很厲害  對吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}She's good, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.95,0:28:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這兒干什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.00,0:28:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于案件調查...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}As for the investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.52,0:28:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一夫人需要支持\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}First Lady wanted some support.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.02,0:28:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...聯調局反恐處處長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}...the FBI director of counterterrorism
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.00,0:28:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會向大家進行全面匯報  但是...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}will give you a full briefing. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.97,0:29:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為有必要親自澄清\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I feel it's important to personally address
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.04,0:29:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在古德溫先生住所找到的文件\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}the document found in Mr. Goodwin's residence
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.16,0:29:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次發布會前剛剛發到大家手上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that was made available to you just before this conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.80,0:29:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多措辭足以成為引人注目的頭條新聞\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's filled with language that would make for flashy headlines,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.01,0:29:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如謀殺  腐敗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}words like "murder," "corruption."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.61,0:29:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中指控總統與彼得·羅素和\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The accusation that the President was involved in the deaths
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.30,0:29:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐伊·巴恩斯的死有關\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}of Peter Russo and Zoe Barnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.12,0:29:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有"濫用職權"這樣的字眼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Phrases like "abuse of power,"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.64,0:29:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡管這一切沒有事實依據\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}while they have no basis in reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.95,0:29:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻讓我們悲哀地一窺他飽受困擾的內心\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}they do give us a sad glimpse into a very troubled mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.17,0:29:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And it pains me that anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.43,0:29:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是有精神疾病的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}even someone who is mentally ill,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.16,0:29:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真會相信古德溫先生對我丈夫的指控\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}would think my husband is capable of
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.94,0:29:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那會讓我十分痛心\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}what Mr.Goodwin believed to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.38,0:29:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但最讓我心痛的是古德溫先生的父母\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But mostly it pains me for Mr. Goodwin's parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.42,0:29:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們還在應對失去兒子的痛苦\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}who are coping with the loss of their son.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.84,0:29:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據大家說  他一生中大部分時候是個好人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And, by all accounts, he was a decent man for most of his life,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.41,0:29:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但顯然  他內心的什么地方崩潰了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but clearly, something snapped in him
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.50,0:29:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他迫切需要的時候沒能得到幫助\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and he never got the help he so desperately needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.55,0:29:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我懇請大家尊重他的父母\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So I ask that all of you respect his parents' grief
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.68,0:30:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要對這個生病的年輕人的話加以渲染\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}by not sensationalizing the words of a sick young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.94,0:30:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們記住勞倫斯和貝蒂·密查姆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And let's remember Lawrence and Betty Meechum,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.46,0:30:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的兒子艾德華\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}whose son Edward
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.16,0:30:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為古德溫先生的病獻出了自己的生命\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}gave his life because of Mr. Goodwin's illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.72,0:30:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德華的犧牲是我丈夫還活著的唯一原因\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Edward's sacrifice is the only reason my husband is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.57,0:30:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會永遠感激\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And I'll be forever grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.87,0:30:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的友誼和奉獻\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}for his friendship and his devoted service.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.99,0:30:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.49,0:30:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反恐處處長納森·格林\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Counterterrorism Director Nathan Green.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.31,0:30:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天調查取得了新進展\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Today we had a new development in the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.70,0:30:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天下午我們詢問了司法部長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This afternoon, we interviewed the Attorney General.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.35,0:30:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她告訴了我們她和希瑟·鄧巴\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}She gave us a full account of a conversation she had
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.92,0:30:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在槍擊當天進行的談話的全部內容\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}with Heather Dunbar the day of the shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.31,0:30:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,談話中  鄧巴女士聲稱\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}In this conversation, Ms. Dunbar claimed to have met
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.88,0:30:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾親自見過盧卡斯·古德溫\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}with Lucas Goodwin personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.29,0:30:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們雖沒有理由相信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And while we have no reason to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.98,0:30:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鄧巴女士和刺殺企圖有任何關系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Ms. Dunbar had anything to do with the assassination attempt...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.33,0:30:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會就這場聲稱的談話對她進行質詢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}we will be questioning her about this alleged conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.05,0:30:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要抓她嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Are you arresting her?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.17,0:30:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  女士  我們只是來問幾個問題\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, ma'am. We're here to ask a few questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.98,0:30:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那你需要提出正式請求  -她現在在嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Then you need to make a formal request. - Is she here now?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.80,0:31:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接把請求發給我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Send the request directly to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.40,0:31:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會和鄧巴女士的律師討論\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and then I'll discuss it with Ms. Dunbar's attorneys.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.63,0:31:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱特\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Hey, Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.71,0:31:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你打過電話  固話和手機\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I tried calling. Home and cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.11,0:31:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,座機線拔了  手機關機了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Pulled out the cord. Turned off the cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.46,0:31:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我這種人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Because of people like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.49,0:31:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人至少有禮貌沒跑來我家門口\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The others had the courtesy not to show up on my doorstep.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.28,0:31:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禮貌從沒幫我達成什么目的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Courtesy never got me anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.29,0:31:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們能談談嗎  私下談\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Can we talk? Off the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.15,0:31:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是你的話...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If it were anyone but you...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.60,0:31:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸運的是  是我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, luckily, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.89,0:31:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去牽福斯托  該遛他了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let me get Fausto. It's time for his walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.75,0:31:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是核行業的  不是化石燃料\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm in the nuclear game, not fossil fuels.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.50,0:31:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人有你在中國那樣的關系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No one has the relationships you do in China.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.49,0:31:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中國人已經跟我撇清關系了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Chinese disowned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.07,0:31:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們會回心轉意的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They'll come around.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.19,0:31:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰讓你來的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Who put you up to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.21,0:31:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要開自己的公司\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Starting my own firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.42,0:32:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為你不干了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I thought you were out?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.57,0:32:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那是在自欺欺人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I was fooling myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.73,0:32:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統剛被槍擊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So, president gets shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.63,0:32:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就忍不住要趁火打劫了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and you just can't help taking advantage of the chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.01,0:32:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所說的火  我稱之為機遇\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What you call chaos, I call opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.39,0:32:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的第一位客戶\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And you're my first client.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.26,0:32:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你好運\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I wish you the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.23,0:32:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不是你的第一位客戶\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But I'm not your first client.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.37,0:32:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想跟白宮扯上關系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't wanna have anything to do with the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.61,0:32:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你因為沃克的丑聞損失了很多錢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You lost a lot of money during the Walker scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.57,0:32:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  正因此我才要拒絕你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I did, indeed, which is why I'm turning you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.35,0:32:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉你跑了這么大老遠結果被拒絕\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm sorry you came all the way out here for a "No."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.83,0:32:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想進監獄吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You don't wanna go to prison, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.56,0:32:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再失去僅剩的一切\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Lose the rest of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.90,0:32:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經被赦免了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've already been pardoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.76,0:33:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免的是洗錢罪  不是偽證罪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}For the money laundering, not for perjury.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.01,0:33:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說沃克知道  但是他不知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You said that Walker knew, and he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.45,0:33:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有說你當時在跟弗蘭克合作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What you didn't say is that you were working with Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.36,0:33:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家憑什么相信你而不是我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Why should anybody believe you more than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.81,0:33:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要么賭一把\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You take that chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.63,0:33:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后看著克雷頓-維斯特變成低價股\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and watch Clayton West become a penny stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.12,0:33:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么我們成為終結石油危機的英雄\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Or we're heroes for ending the oil crisis,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.46,0:33:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都發財  你也能重樹形象\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}everybody gets rich, your image is restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.58,0:33:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們也許還會讓你選\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They'll probably even let you choose
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.97,0:33:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一任駐北京的大使\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}the next ambassador in Beijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.19,0:33:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并不認為那有一絲真實性\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So you don't think any of it is true?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.43,0:33:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.04,0:33:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想相信他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And I wanted to believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.51,0:33:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那第一夫人淚眼汪汪說的那些話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So the First Lady's whole teary-eyed thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.71,0:33:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得她是對的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I think she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.50,0:33:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盧卡斯是哪里崩潰了吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Something in Lucas snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.40,0:33:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認識的盧卡斯不會想殺死總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I mean, the Lucas I knew wouldn't have tried to kill a president.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.37,0:34:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  我就是這意思\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Exactly. That's my point.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.40,0:34:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真覺得安德伍德殺過人嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You honestly think Underwood was murdering people?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.99,0:34:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的懷疑態度哪去了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Where is your skepticism?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.48,0:34:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懷疑盧卡斯  也懷疑白宮\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm skeptical of Lucas and I'm skeptical of the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.89,0:34:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么沒證據\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How come there's no proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.73,0:34:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點沒有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}None.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.05,0:34:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盧卡斯試了  我也試了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}After Lucas tried, after I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.80,0:34:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的建議是算了吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}My advice is to let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.21,0:34:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只會重復我們的徒勞\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're gonna repeat the same goose chase we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.85,0:34:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總得問一下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I had to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.18,0:34:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你的編輯怎么說  -說算了吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- What does your editor say? - To let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.27,0:34:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.74,0:34:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他可不如你  -那是我以前\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- He's not as good as you are. - Was.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.65,0:34:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望你在《電訊報》工作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Wish you were at The Telegraph.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.14,0:34:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  要是有人被開了就告訴我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yeah, let me know if anyone gets fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.84,0:34:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,門沒關\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.64,0:34:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一收到你的短信就盡快趕過來了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I came as soon as I got your text.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.25,0:35:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發布會后我們忙得不可開交\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We've been slammed since the press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.37,0:35:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況怎么樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How's it lookin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.61,0:35:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鄧巴的事大受關注\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Major play on the Dunbar story.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.08,0:35:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓第一夫人去說是個好主意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It was a good idea to have the First Lady talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.46,0:35:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要喝蘇打水嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You want a soda?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.77,0:35:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來杯水什么的嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}A glass of water or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.48,0:35:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水就好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Water's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.22,0:35:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已決定讓你留下了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've decided you can stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.24,0:35:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道格  我希望你能理解\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Doug, I hope you can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.55,0:35:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我緊張了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I got nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.34,0:35:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時情況看起來不太好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You know, things weren't looking good and...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.14,0:35:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想留條退路  以防萬一\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}yeah, I wanted an out, in case I needed one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.25,0:35:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那的確是個錯誤  我希望我沒有那樣做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I mean, it was a mistake. I wish I hadn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.10,0:35:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你糾正了你的錯誤\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You corrected your mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.32,0:35:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那才是最重要的  要冰塊嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That's all that matters. You want ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.47,0:35:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.97,0:35:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在不能讓競選再出現問題了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We can't afford any more shake-ups in the campaign right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.61,0:35:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其總統還在醫院里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}especially with the president in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.26,0:36:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也不能讓你再犯錯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We also can't afford any more of your mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.68,0:36:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴  閉嘴\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Shut up. Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.46,0:36:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛醒來的時候  說不出話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}When I first woke up, I couldn't speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.98,0:36:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得眨眼來表達我的反應\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I had to blink my eyes if I wanted to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.92,0:36:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.14,0:36:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我得不到你的忠誠\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If I can't get your loyalty,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.03,0:36:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就要你順從\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I will have your obedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.30,0:36:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眨眼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Blink.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.95,0:36:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眨眼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Blink!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.28,0:36:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.00,0:36:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Fucking...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.48,0:36:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.61,0:36:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有病  伙計\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're fucked up, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.29,0:37:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-別叫了  -早上好  漢默施密特先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Quit it. - Good morning, Mr. Hammerschmidt.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.19,0:37:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.04,0:37:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來還你的筆記\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Uh, we're just returning your notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.51,0:37:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們復印過了  這是原件\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We made copies. These are the originals.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.95,0:37:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很有用吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Nothing too useful, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.35,0:37:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  先生  但還是感謝你的配合\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, sir, but thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.56,0:37:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有你的報紙  放在臺階上的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Your paper, too. It was on the step.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.12,0:37:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你今天愉快  漢默施密特先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, you have a good day, Mr. Hammerschmidt.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.44,0:37:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.45,0:37:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要告訴我你又餓了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Don't tell me you're hungry already.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.84,0:37:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才喂過你  天吶\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I just fed you. Good God.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.23,0:37:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了  來了  來了  來了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm coming. I'm coming, I'm coming, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.86,0:38:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-早上好  -早上好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Morning. - Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.66,0:38:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我建議讓凱茜來做談判\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I suggest we turn the negotiations over to Cathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.46,0:38:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們一直拖著俄羅斯  油價會\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If we keep stalling on Russia, gas prices will--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.42,0:38:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是說這個的時候\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now is not a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.09,0:38:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會讓總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I won't have the president
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.90,0:38:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到一個一片混亂的白宮\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}come back to a White House in disarray.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.62,0:38:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不知道他會不會回來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We don't know that he is coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.12,0:38:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他會的  我向你保證\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He is. I promise you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.89,0:38:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是上帝嗎  你有什么資格保證\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Are you God? Who are you to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.36,0:38:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.00,0:38:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔斯克先生和丹頓先生來了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mr. Tusk and Mr. Danton are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.22,0:38:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他們進來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Send them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.48,0:38:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早安排的  我們要討論俄羅斯的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It was arranged this morning. We're discussing Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.91,0:38:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  我是幕僚長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Sir, I am the Chief of Staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.45,0:38:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些事情你必須讓我知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You have to keep me informed of these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.22,0:39:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.25,0:39:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我覺得應該是你要聽我的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but I believe you answer to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.89,0:39:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是反過來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}not the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.14,0:39:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國務卿杜蘭特應該參加這個會\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Secretary Durant should be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.81,0:39:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是一次私下碰面\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This meeting is private.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.92,0:39:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之后會跟你們倆討論\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll discuss it with you both after.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.35,0:39:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統絕不會允許雷蒙德\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The president would never allow Raymond--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.31,0:39:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-總統先生  -塔斯克先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Mr. President. - Mr. Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.91,0:39:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷米  很高興見到你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Remy, good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.97,0:39:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-總統先生  -斯坦普先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Mr. President. - Mr. Stamper.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.93,0:39:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們稍后繼續  道格\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll follow up with you later, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.80,0:39:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.17,0:39:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝您這么快就抽出時間見我們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thanks for taking the time to meet with us on such short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.04,0:39:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石油的問題沒時間可以浪費了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, there's no time to waste on this oil thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.80,0:39:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟中國那邊有了些進展\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've made some progress with the Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.64,0:39:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  第一夫人現在在里面\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Sir, the First Lady is in there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.21,0:39:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在等我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}She's expecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.48,0:39:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還想贏得選舉呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We're trying to win an election,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.59,0:39:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你卻想提醒所有人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and you want to remind everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.62,0:39:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統赦免了雷蒙德·塔斯克\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that the president pardoned Raymond Tusk?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.64,0:39:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們換個地方說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let's find somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.28,0:39:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都是國家大事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}These are matters of state.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.97,0:39:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你無權干涉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You don't have the authority to intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.48,0:39:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果唐納德想聽我的建議  那他就有權這么做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If Donald wants my counsel, that is his prerogative.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.92,0:39:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你故意騙我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You are deliberately deceiving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.50,0:39:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你背著我  -你忘了你的身份  道格拉斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Going behind my-- - You have forgotten your place, Douglas.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.53,0:40:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身份  那你呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}My place? What about your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.06,0:40:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在他最需要你時離開  還威脅他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You leave him when he needs you most, you threaten him,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.95,0:40:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在他進了醫院  你還拆他的臺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and now that he's in here, you undermine him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.17,0:40:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你應該  -別說了  夠了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- You're supposed to be-- - Stop. That is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.68,0:40:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會告訴你一切\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I will fill you in on everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.36,0:40:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不是在這兒  而是在白宮\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but not here. At the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.07,0:40:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.47,0:40:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的心臟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}His heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.80,0:40:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-醫生  -他有些偶發心律不齊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Doctor? - He's had some sporadic arrhythmia.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.83,0:40:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-請出去一下好嗎  -好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Will you give us the room for a moment? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.69,0:40:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不能一直斗下去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We can't keep battling each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.25,0:40:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他都這樣子了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}not with him like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.23,0:40:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要一條新的道路\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We need a new path forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.41,0:40:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能幫忙\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and I would like your help with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.46,0:40:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保證不會瞞著你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I promise I won't keep you in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.92,0:40:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你準備好  我們白宮見\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll meet you at the White House whenever you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.67,0:40:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要留在這里  我覺得這更重要\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm staying here. I think this is more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.65,0:40:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.61,0:41:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德伍德夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mrs. Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.41,0:41:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關于如何對付俄羅斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mr. Tusk and Mr. Danton have a proposal
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.46,0:41:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔斯克先生和丹頓先生有個提議\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}about how to deal with Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.91,0:41:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您今天最沒想到會見到的就是我吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I imagine I'm the last person you expected to see today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.32,0:41:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見到你們二位\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I am a bit surprised,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.43,0:41:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的確有些驚訝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}yes, to see both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.00,0:41:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家對我們的到來肯定都有些警覺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm sure there's some wariness about us being here,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.24,0:41:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們有個對付俄羅斯的好計劃\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but I think we have a good plan on how to handle Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.67,0:41:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想加入嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Would you like to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.84,0:41:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓雷蒙德給你詳說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Raymond can lay it out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.05,0:41:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道我能提供些什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, I don't know what I can offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.60,0:41:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我又開始跟白宮合作的消息傳出去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, we're going to catch some flack if word gets out
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.36,0:41:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們肯定要受到抨擊的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that I'm back in business with the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.38,0:41:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以幫我們平息那些聲音\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You could help us smooth that over.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.67,0:41:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的新聞發布會相當感人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Your press conference was very moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.01,0:41:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-弗蘭克的事  我很遺憾  -謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- I'm sorry about Frank. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.82,0:41:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然  他要是知道我進了總統辦公室\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Of course, he'd have a conniption fit
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.40,0:41:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會大發脾氣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}if he knew I were in the Oval Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.44,0:41:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是個實用主義者  雷蒙德  只要成功就行\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, he is a pragmatist, Raymond. Whatever works.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.58,0:41:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我們繼續吧  -雷米\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Shall we continue? - Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.37,0:41:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,計劃是提出建立\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So, the plan is to propose a partnership
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.49,0:42:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美中能源公司合作伙伴關系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}between American and Chinese energy companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.78,0:42:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有點緊張\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You seem nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.20,0:42:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一陣子沒見了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.71,0:43:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該怎么辦  老大\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What should I do, boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.41,0:43:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薩克遜醫生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Dr. Saxon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.23,0:43:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想捐肝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'd like to donate.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.49,0:43:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-斯坦普先生  -我是O型血\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Mr. Stamper-- - My blood type is O.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.80,0:43:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很健康  我們開始做測試吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm healthy. Let's do the tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.95,0:43:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,健康不是捐肝的唯一標準\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That's not the only criteria for donation.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.12,0:43:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是個正在戒酒的酗酒者  我們不接受\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're a recovering alcoholic. We don't accept--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.02,0:43:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管什么規則\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't care about the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.92,0:43:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我配型成功  我希望你能做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If I'm a match, I want you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.22,0:43:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算成功了  也幫不上忙\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Even if you were, it wouldn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.90,0:43:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已經病得太重  只有部分肝臟不夠\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's too ill for a partial liver at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.13,0:43:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他需要一整個\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He needs a full one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.49,0:43:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  但我們只能等待并企盼了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm sorry, but we'll just have to wait and hope.
